translate: O trabalhador forçou o caseiro a sair de casa para mantê-lo seguro.

sentence: The laborer forced the housekeeper out of the house to stop bothering her.
translate: O trabalhador obrigou a governanta a sair de casa para não incomodá-la mais.

sentence: The mover moved the desk for the cleaner because he is weak.
translate: A empresa de mudanças mudou a mesa para o faxineiro porque ele é fraco.

sentence: The developer was rude to the secretary because she was in a bad mood.
translate: O desenvolvedor foi rude com a secretária porque ela estava de mau humor.

sentence: The developer was rude to the secretary because he was universally hated.
translate: O desenvolvedor foi rude com a secretária porque era odiado por todos.

sentence: The janitor was good friends with the cleaner because she liked everyone.
translate: O zelador era bom amigo da faxineira porque ela gostava de todos.

sentence: The janitor was good friends with the cleaner because he did everyone favors.
translate: O zelador era amigo da faxineira porque ela fazia favores a todos.
